thread.title: Larry Daniel

author: Larry Daniel
title: Larry Daniel
text:
While we admittedly a new entrant into the Call center space, our management has been in technology for over two decades and has brought multiple companies through acquisition cycle, so we've had ample time and experience evaluating business partners. We've been impressed with five9 - both the product and support services have matched or exceeded our expectations.
Especially given the pricing, we so no need to consider any other call center platforms.
